{{Top|leg}}
'''Klatooinian''' language was once the native language of the [[Klatooinian/Legends|Klatooinians]], the native people of [[Klatooine/Legends|Klatooine]]. By the latter days of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], it was a dead language.<ref name="u">''[[Ultimate Alien Anthology]]''</ref>

After the beginning of Klatooinian servitude to [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]] circa [[25,100 BBY]], the Klatooinian language was increasingly forgotten. In a few years, Klatooinians began to speak only [[Huttese/Legends|Huttese]], and most of them were illiterate. The Klatooinian language only existed in ancient texts, and was known mostly by (non-Klatooinian) scholars. This was an anomaly in Klatooinian culture, which was otherwise highly concerned with preserving its ancient traditions.<ref name="u" />

